Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:02.76,中文,,0,0,0,,前情提要\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Previously on The Strain...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.76,0:00:04.69,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸 发生了什么事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dad, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.69,0:00:07.61,中文,,0,0,0,,这是我们正在调查的传染病的一部分\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This is part of the epidemic we've been investigating.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.91,0:00:09.41,中文,,0,0,0,,马特被感染了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Matt was infected.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.41,0:00:10.22,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我要你告诉我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now I need you to tell me:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.22,0:00:12.10,中文,,0,0,0,,你上次和你妈妈联系是什么时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when was the last time you heard from your mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.10,0:00:12.95,中文,,0,0,0,,今天上午\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.95,0:00:15.93,中文,,0,0,0,,他们正在为你争吵 因为你要我们去佛蒙特州\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They were arguing about you because you told us to go to Vermont.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.94,0:00:17.62,中文,,0,0,0,,马特昨晚甚至没有回家\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Matt didn't even come home last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.62,0:00:19.26,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道艾尔德里奇 帕尔默是谁吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Do you know who Eldritch Palmer is?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.26,0:00:21.40,中文,,0,0,0,,世界上最有权势的人之一 是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}One of the most powerful men in the world, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.40,0:00:22.47,中文,,0,0,0,,他雇佣了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He hired me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.47,0:00:23.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你干了什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:25.85,中文,,0,0,0,,我尽我最大的能力瘫痪了因特网\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I worked my ass off to shut the internet down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.85,0:00:27.05,中文,,0,0,0,,我们可以找到血祖\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We can get the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.05,0:00:29.08,中文,,0,0,0,,他闭不出户 就在这个城市的某个地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's nesting. Somewhere in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.08,0:00:30.20,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我需要你的帮助\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But I need your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:30.87,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉在哪儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where's Kelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.87,0:00:32.44,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉失联一整天了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kelly's MIA all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:33.64,中文,,0,0,0,,扎克在哪 伊弗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Where's Zack, Eph?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.64,0:00:34.62,中文,,0,0,0,,他和我的同事们在一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}He's with my colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.62,0:00:35.66,中文,,0,0,0,,这里不安全\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's not safe here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.66,0:00:38.08,中文,,0,0,0,,对啊 对啊 在你觉得事态如此严重的时候\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Right, right. In all your concerned state,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.08,0:00:39.95,中文,,0,0,0,,还能抽时间滚床单\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}you still find time to screw on the rug.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.95,0:00:41.99,中文,,0,0,0,,她说真的 你必须尽快地离开这个镇子\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's serious. You have to get out of town as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.00,0:00:45.04,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 你伤害了我的朋友 我会挖出你的心的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. You hurt my friend, I will cut your heart out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.04,0:00:48.07,中文,,0,0,0,,我爱我的妻子 他是我儿子的母亲\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I love my wife. She's the mother of my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:49.81,中文,,0,0,0,,我会不惜一切来找到她的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'd do anything to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.14,0:01:47.81,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.86,0:01:57.13,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 该死\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Aw, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.85,0:02:32.05,中文,,0,0,0,,不 拜托 拜托了 给力点啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, come on! Please! Work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.49,0:02:40.45,中文,,0,0,0,,好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:47.54,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸 爸爸 来这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dad! Dad, come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.47,0:02:50.65,中文,,0,0,0,,- 怎么了 出了什么事 - 妈妈的手机 它动了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What is it? What's wrong? - Mom's phone, it moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.65,0:02:52.38,中文,,0,0,0,,- 她在移动 - 你在说什么呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- She's moving. - What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:54.40,中文,,0,0,0,,几个月前我丢失了我的手机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I lost my phone a couple months ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我用这个网站来追踪它\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I used this website to track it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.79,0:02:58.18,中文,,0,0,0,,所以我想 你明白的 或许我们可以用这个来追踪她\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So I thought, you know, maybe we could use it on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.18,0:02:59.27,中文,,0,0,0,,你能上网了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got online?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.27,0:03:02.43,中文,,0,0,0,,几乎上不了 它超级慢 但是我最终找到了信号\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Barely. It's super slow, but I finally got enough of a signal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:05.25,中文,,0,0,0,,信号时有时无 但是也足够我监测到手机的移动了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's going in and out but I got enough to see the phone move.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.19,0:03:11.54,中文,,0,0,0,,- 你确定它正在移动吗 - 是的 大概是3个街区\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- You're sure it's moving? - Yeah. Like 3 blocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.54,0:03:13.91,中文,,0,0,0,,如果她正在移动 那她就应该还好 对吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If she's moving, she's gotta be ok, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.78,0:03:17.41,中文,,0,0,0,,- 这是个好的现象 - 我要给她打电话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- It's a good sign. - I'm going to call her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.77,0:03:30.86,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸 手机响了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dad, it's ringing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.17,0:03:33.94,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 我是凯莉 请留言\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hi, it's Kelly. Leave me a message
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.94,0:03:36.02,中文,,0,0,0,,我尽快回复你的 谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and I'll call you right back. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:39.03,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈 又是我 给我回电话 好吗 拜托了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mom, it's me again. Call me back, ok? Please?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.52,0:03:42.68,中文,,0,0,0,,或许她的手机是静音或者别的什么状态\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe it's on silent or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:46.63,中文,,0,0,0,,为什么她还不打回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why hasn't she called back?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.47,0:03:52.21,中文,,0,0,0,,- 她在哪片区域 - 这里显示是在\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- What was the location? - This says...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:54.21,中文,,0,0,0,,在主街和前街的交叉口\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Main and Front.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.55,0:03:59.51,中文,,0,0,0,,- 不 拜托了 拜托 快动啊 - 嘘 没事的 没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- No! Come on, please! Work! - Shh. It's ok. It's ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:01.06,中文,,0,0,0,,我们已经知道她的位置了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We know her location.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.61,0:04:04.87,中文,,0,0,0,,我会找到她的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll get her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.33,0:04:29.63,中文,,0,0,0,,总统已经宣布了所有银行停业\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The President has declared a bank holiday in an attempt
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:32.95,中文,,0,0,0,,旨在稳定国家震荡的金融系统\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}to stabilize the nation's teetering financial system.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.95,0:04:34.00,中文,,0,0,0,,最新的政策随着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This latest move comes
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.00,0:04:37.15,中文,,0,0,0,,昨日23家银行于昨日倒闭而发布了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}in the wake of 23 bank failures yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:38.20,中文,,0,0,0,,尽管已经有这些措施\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Despite these measures,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.20,0:04:40.63,中文,,0,0,0,,国际货币基金组织首脑\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the head of the International Monetary Fund
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.79,中文,,0,0,0,,在今天的新闻发布会上透露\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}hinted in a news conference today
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.79,0:04:45.49,中文,,0,0,0,,世界金融系统依旧在震荡\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}that the world financial system is now teetering
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.49,0:04:48.04,中文,,0,0,0,,- 正濒临系统 - 发生了什么事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- on the brink of systematic-- - What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.52,0:04:52.75,中文,,0,0,0,,扎克追踪到了凯莉的手机了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Zack tracked down Kelly's phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.68,0:04:55.85,中文,,0,0,0,,这就是你爱的那个男人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.90,0:04:58.48,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈先把你的茶喝掉吧 别凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.79,0:04:59.94,中文,,0,0,0,,早上好 马丁内兹夫人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Good morning, Mrs. Martinez.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.94,0:05:01.63,中文,,0,0,0,,手机正在移动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The phone is moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.83,0:05:04.16,中文,,0,0,0,,- 在哪儿 - 阿斯托利亚\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Where is it? - Astoria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.31,0:05:06.30,中文,,0,0,0,,- 别说了 - 我没打算说了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Don't say it. - I wasn't gonna.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.30,0:05:07.99,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉可能还活着\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kelly could be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.56,0:05:10.74,中文,,0,0,0,,手机在白天移动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The phone is moving during daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:12.82,中文,,0,0,0,,她可能已经出来了而没有被困住 我们做到了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She could've gotten out without getting stung. We did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:14.66,中文,,0,0,0,,他们正在动员楼下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They're mobilizing downstairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.67,0:05:15.81,中文,,0,0,0,,塞特拉基安有个计划\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Setrakian has a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:17.58,中文,,0,0,0,,我必须要先干这件事了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I have to do this first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.08,0:05:23.70,中文,,0,0,0,,昨晚我并不是想要伤害你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I didn't mean to hurt you last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:25.35,中文,,0,0,0,,都是些没意义的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing makes any sense anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.35,0:05:26.40,中文,,0,0,0,,我当时不知道我在说些什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't know what I'm saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:29.82,中文,,0,0,0,,我在做些什么 但是我后来知道了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}what I'm doing, but I knew what I was doing then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.82,0:05:33.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我并不为此感到后悔\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.22,0:05:36.71,中文,,0,0,0,,我知道你想要为我做最坏的打算\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I know you tried to prepare me for the worst
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:38.45,中文,,0,0,0,,但是我认为现在有一个真正的机会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}but I think there's a real chance here
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:42.23,中文,,0,0,0,,- 而只要有 - 你就会去尝试\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- and so long as there is-- - Then you should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:49.42,中文,,0,0,0,,但是你必须为你可能找到的东西做好准备\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But you must be prepared for what you might find.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.40,0:05:51.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我明白\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:55.76,中文,,0,0,0,,带上你的武器\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Take your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:08.83,中文,,0,0,0,,- 有什么变化吗 - 还是在相同的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Any change? - Still in the same place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:10.77,中文,,0,0,0,,我不能一起去吗 我不想就只是坐在这儿\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Can't I come? I don't want to just sit here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.77,0:06:12.52,中文,,0,0,0,,不 我需要你追踪手机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, I need you to track the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.52,0:06:14.21,中文,,0,0,0,,如果信号移动了就发短信给我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Text me if the signal moves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:15.86,中文,,0,0,0,,如果短信联系不上呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What if it doesn't go through?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.86,0:06:17.13,中文,,0,0,0,,那就一直发\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep texting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.51,中文,,0,0,0,,把妈妈带回来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Bring mom back with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.78,0:06:28.35,中文,,0,0,0,,我追踪到没有老鼠的区域的中心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I tracked the epicenter of the rat-free zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.35,0:06:30.52,中文,,0,0,0,,正好就在世贸中心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Right down here by the World Trade Center.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.52,0:06:32.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我钻到这些管道里面去调查\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I popped down into the tunnels to investigate,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:37.41,中文,,0,0,0,,最终和几打吸血鬼面对面了 真是愉快的一天\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}ended up eye-to-eye with a few dozen of them. It was a fun day.
