Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.71,0:20:27.94,中文,,0,0,0,,真的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Really? Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.41,0:20:30.33,中文,,0,0,0,,倒是进展的蛮快的啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Seemed to have such a shorthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:35.16,中文,,0,0,0,,你呢 你又是什么来历\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What about you? What's your story?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.41,0:20:39.35,中文,,0,0,0,,没什么来历 就如你所见\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No story. What you see is what you get.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:45.34,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 亲爱的 当铺那家伙是个吸血鬼猎人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Listen, honey. The pawn shop guy is a vampire killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.70,0:20:50.09,中文,,0,0,0,,如果你神秘的背景比他的更来来头的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you could top that story with your mysterious background,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.09,0:20:52.12,中文,,0,0,0,,那就 说出来吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then... go for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:57.14,中文,,0,0,0,,好吧 你想知道什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Fine. What do you want to know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:20:59.37,中文,,0,0,0,,帕尔默这家伙\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This guy Palmer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.34,0:21:03.20,中文,,0,0,0,,找你去开启世界末日\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Guy dicks you over to bring about end times?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.97,0:21:07.92,中文,,0,0,0,,如果我们只是去趟他的老窝蹭点无线网\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If we're going to his building just to borrow his wifi
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.92,0:21:10.30,中文,,0,0,0,,那你就是在浪费我的时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then you're wasting my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:17.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我肯定不会浪费你的时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I wouldn't dream of wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:30.51,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\pos(882,512)}{\fade(0,500)}石心集团 曼哈顿  57西街156号
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.43,0:21:32.37,中文,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:35.33,中文,,0,0,0,,纽约虫害控制中心\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Uh, New York Pest Control Services.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:39.20,中文,,0,0,0,,我们要检查一下你们的行政餐饮设施\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We have to inspect your executive dining facilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.15,0:21:42.75,中文,,0,0,0,,我没有找到你的预约\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't have you down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.04,0:21:44.15,中文,,0,0,0,,我们检查都不让\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well they don't let us
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.15,0:21:46.38,中文,,0,0,0,,事先预约的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}make appointments for inspections, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.24,0:21:49.86,中文,,0,0,0,,没有保全系统确认 我不能让你进去的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I can't let you through without an OK from security.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.68,0:21:52.33,中文,,0,0,0,,你确定吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.50,0:21:55.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我们只是快速的看一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's pretty much just a quick look-see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.13,0:21:58.79,中文,,0,0,0,,我们只是需要应付一下我麻烦的领导\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know, another box I have to check off for my hard-ass boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.99,0:22:00.60,中文,,0,0,0,,10分钟内就能完事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In and out in 10?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:08.95,中文,,0,0,0,,嗯 行政餐饮中心好像正在换班时间\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, it looks like executive dining is in between shifts anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.20,0:22:12.32,中文,,0,0,0,,-所以 哦 太好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- So... - Oh, perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.73,0:22:17.26,中文,,0,0,0,,中间的电梯 25楼\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Middle elevator. 25th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.32,0:22:21.18,中文,,0,0,0,,谢谢洛伦 你最好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thanks Lauren. You're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.18,0:22:23.61,中文,,0,0,0,,祝你一整天都心情愉快 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}And you have yourself a great day, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.65,0:22:26.64,中文,,0,0,0,,-好 -谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Ok. - Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:32.03,中文,,0,0,0,,自信 这一切都来源于自信\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Confidence. It's all about confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.37,0:22:38.49,中文,,0,0,0,,-请跟我们来 好吗 -自信还是自强\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Will you follow us, please? - Confidence or competence?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:45.85,中文,,0,0,0,,听着 我不想找你们的麻烦\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now look, I don't want to get you boys in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.23,0:22:48.88,中文,,0,0,0,,但作为纽约的害虫稽查员\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But as Pest Inspectors for the city of New York,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.88,0:22:52.03,中文,,0,0,0,,我们有权进入任何一家执证经营的食品机构\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}we have the absolute right to enter any licenced food...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.04,0:22:53.58,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 闭嘴\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey. Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.14,0:23:04.48,中文,,0,0,0,,好的 谢谢你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Alright. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.33,0:23:09.70,中文,,0,0,0,,维尔德斯女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ms. Velders.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.86,0:23:12.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我是雷吉 费斯威廉 你还记得我吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Reggie Fitzwilliam, you remember me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.40,0:23:15.12,中文,,0,0,0,,我对你可是印象深刻\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}'Cause I certainly remember you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.84,0:23:17.90,中文,,0,0,0,,看来你改行抓老鼠了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I see you've taken up rat catching.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.90,0:23:19.35,中文,,0,0,0,,看起来是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So it appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.18,0:23:23.33,中文,,0,0,0,,搜他们身\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Search them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.15,0:23:26.36,中文,,0,0,0,,被碰我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.17,0:23:52.31,中文,,0,0,0,,-用这些抓老鼠 -用来对付大只的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Use these for catching rats? - Only really big ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.48,0:23:59.40,中文,,0,0,0,,-现在要怎样 -帕尔默先生要见你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- So what now? - Mr. Palmer would like to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.17,0:24:01.89,中文,,0,0,0,,不 不是你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, not you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.06,0:24:06.21,中文,,0,0,0,,她 单独一人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Her. Alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.05,0:24:45.02,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.18,0:24:55.14,中文,,0,0,0,,你在吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You here?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.56,0:25:08.19,中文,,0,0,0,,我们现在在另一场离奇凶案现场进行直播\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We're live at the scene of of another bizarre murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.19,0:25:10.55,中文,,0,0,0,,今晚这起凶案的不幸遇害者\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}This tragic incident claimed the lives
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.55,0:25:13.52,中文,,0,0,0,,是布鲁克林的一对年轻夫妇\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of a young married couple here in Brooklyn tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.52,0:25:15.69,中文,,0,0,0,,在邻居投诉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}They were found in the basement of their home
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.69,0:25:17.65,中文,,0,0,0,,有一股恶臭传出来之后\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}after a neighbor complained
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.65,0:25:20.71,中文,,0,0,0,,他们在自家的地下室被发现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of a terrible smell emanating from inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.82,0:25:24.77,中文,,0,0,0,,警方表示 一场令人担忧的暴力活动\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Police sources say a disturbing pattern of random violence
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.77,0:25:26.96,中文,,0,0,0,,已经席卷纽约城了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}has swept across New York City.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.96,0:25:30.40,中文,,0,0,0,,近期 警方接到了大量的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}In recent days, police have been inundated with reports
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.40,0:25:32.79,中文,,0,0,0,,入室袭击报警\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of home invasions and attacks...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.07,0:25:42.11,中文,,0,0,0,,我的天啊 我的天啊 凯凯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Oh my God! Oh my God, Kel!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.11,0:25:45.22,中文,,0,0,0,,你吓死我了 几点了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You scared the crap out of me. What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.52,0:25:50.49,中文,,0,0,0,,凯凯\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kel?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.62,0:25:55.59,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kelly?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.97,0:26:02.24,中文,,0,0,0,,这是马特干的吗 你是说真的吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Matt did this? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.21,0:26:07.29,中文,,0,0,0,,-扎克在哪里 -什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Where's Zack...? - What...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.35,0:26:08.49,中文,,0,0,0,,你是说问扎克在哪里吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What do you mean where's zack?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.49,0:26:09.79,中文,,0,0,0,,伊弗说扎克跟他在一起\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Eph said zack was with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.95,0:26:11.72,中文,,0,0,0,,凯凯 亲爱的 你知道吗 你快把我吓死了 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kel, honey, you know what? You're freaking me out, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.72,0:26:14.29,中文,,0,0,0,,我带你去急诊室 好吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}So I'm going to take you to the emergency room, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.82,0:26:15.79,中文,,0,0,0,,妈妈\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.25,0:26:20.52,中文,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What's... What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.37,0:26:32.96,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉 你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kelly! What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.65,0:26:35.97,中文,,0,0,0,,啊 你在干什么啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah! What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.97,0:26:38.83,中文,,0,0,0,,你在干什么 不\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}What are you doing?! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.13,0:27:20.13,中文,,0,0,0,,行了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.56,0:27:32.99,中文,,0,0,0,,天啊 你还回来做什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why in God's name would you ever come back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.99,0:27:35.25,中文,,0,0,0,,因为我不喜欢被欺骗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Because I don't like being taken for a ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.50,0:27:38.72,中文,,0,0,0,,现在我知道帕尔默就是这一切的幕后黑手\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Now I know that Palmer's behind all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.16,0:27:42.98,中文,,0,0,0,,而显然你愿意做他的走狗 但我不愿意\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Evidently you're fine with being his lackey. I am not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.02,0:27:44.74,中文,,0,0,0,,帕尔默先生病得很重\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Mr. Palmer is very ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.74,0:27:47.34,中文,,0,0,0,,我不会让你伤害他的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I won't let you harm him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.73,0:27:50.25,中文,,0,0,0,,要是你敢动他一分一毫\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If you try anything, anything at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.57,0:27:52.04,中文,,0,0,0,,我会杀了你的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.06,0:27:53.41,中文,,0,0,0,,听明白了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Am I clear?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.64,0:28:13.11,中文,,0,0,0,,维尔德斯女士 应邀前来了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ms. Valders. As requested.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.76,0:28:15.24,中文,,0,0,0,,维尔德斯女士\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Ah. Ms. Valders.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.08,0:28:18.60,中文,,0,0,0,,我很佩服你的勇气\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I so admire your pluck.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.60,0:28:21.64,中文,,0,0,0,,你以为你和 那个谁 一个抓老鼠的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Thinking you and...who? A rat catcher?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.64,0:28:24.43,中文,,0,0,0,,能来着 然后怎样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Could come here and...What?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.44,0:28:26.55,中文,,0,0,0,,除掉我吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dispense with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.04,0:28:30.37,中文,,0,0,0,,如此愚蠢可笑的计划真是令人震惊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The mind boggles at the absurdity of the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.37,0:28:33.85,中文,,0,0,0,,但计划背后的你们 还挺大胆的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But the ego behind it... Audacious.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.85,0:28:35.11,中文,,0,0,0,,你骗了我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You lied to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.96,0:28:39.96,中文,,0,0,0,,我们当时可是做了交易的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Did we have a deeper transaction than I recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.45,0:28:44.75,中文,,0,0,0,,-我花钱买了你 你帮我完成事情 -你也是个吸血鬼吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I bought you. You let me. - Are you a vampire, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.20,0:28:46.49,中文,,0,0,0,,完全不是\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hardly.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.11,0:28:51.67,中文,,0,0,0,,你想要毁灭世界 让人类灭绝\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You wanted to bring the world down. Wipe out the human race.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.67,0:28:53.88,中文,,0,0,0,,一个有理智的人会干这种事吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Why would any rational person want to do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.88,0:28:56.80,中文,,0,0,0,,首先 不要否认你自己在这件事上的功劳\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}First, don't deny yourself due credit.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.80,0:29:00.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你可以鞠躬谢幕了 你做的很出色\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You should be taking a bow. You did exceptional work.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.56,0:29:04.02,中文,,0,0,0,,说真的 没有你这件事我做不来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Truly. I couldn't have done this without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.41,0:29:09.00,中文,,0,0,0,,人类的DNA随着年龄的增长而衰退\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Human DNA decays as we age.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.00,0:29:11.47,中文,,0,0,0,,随着时间的流逝 它会受损 会衰退\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Over time, it frays and it fails
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.47,0:29:13.73,中文,,0,0,0,,我们的生命也随之逝去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and we follow suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.90,0:29:16.83,中文,,0,0,0,,但是 遗传的密码可以被重写\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}But, it's a code that can be rewritten.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.83,0:29:20.27,中文,,0,0,0,,就像你重新编程软件然后就能掌控硬件\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rewrite the software and you control the hardware:
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.27,0:29:23.70,中文,,0,0,0,,也就是人类的肌肉和组织\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The meat, muscle, and tissue that is mankind.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.70,0:29:24.51,中文,,0,0,0,,目的是什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}To what end?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.52,0:29:29.23,中文,,0,0,0,,如果黑客入侵是为了探索可能性的极限\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}If hacking is about exploring the limits of what is possible,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.48,0:29:33.03,中文,,0,0,0,,那么 我的目的 用你的话来说\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}then I am on the verge of achieving what you would consider
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.04,0:29:35.47,中文,,0,0,0,,就是终极入侵\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}the ultimate hack.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.77,0:29:41.07,中文,,0,0,0,,-欺骗死神 -长生不老\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Cheating death. - Immortality?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.62,0:29:42.79,中文,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.80,0:29:46.06,中文,,0,0,0,,-非常感谢你的分享 -梦想即将实现\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Well thanks for sharing. - It's hard to be on the verge
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.06,0:29:47.39,中文,,0,0,0,,的喜悦很难\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}of something so exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.39,0:29:49.67,中文,,0,0,0,,不跟别人分享\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}and not share the good news with someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.67,0:29:53.10,中文,,0,0,0,,-而你是最佳人选 -为什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- And you are the perfect person. - And how's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.10,0:29:55.48,中文,,0,0,0,,因为 就是你说出去 谁又会相信呢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Well, who would listen to you if you shared it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.48,0:29:57.70,中文,,0,0,0,,你不过是名无名小卒\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You are insignificant.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.15,0:30:00.89,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道你自己有多么不起眼的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You feel how invisible you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.40,0:30:04.31,中文,,0,0,0,,所以你才为我做了那些事\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's why you did what you did for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.63,0:30:07.74,中文,,0,0,0,,-我说得对吗 -狗惹的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Am I right about that? - Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.76,0:30:11.01,中文,,0,0,0,,你 你浑蛋 放开我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You...you asshole! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.66,0:30:13.80,中文,,0,0,0,,你什么也不是 你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're the nothing. You.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.17,0:30:16.98,中文,,0,0,0,,-我们不想再见到她了 -放开我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- We won't see her again. - Get off me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.98,0:30:18.20,中文,,0,0,0,,不 先生 你不会再见到她了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No, sir. You will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.20,0:30:19.62,中文,,0,0,0,,放开我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Get off me!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.84,0:30:29.34,中文,,0,0,0,,{\fs50\fn微软雅黑\bord0\b1\pos(636,520)}{\fade(0,500)}15小时之前
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.14,0:30:34.76,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kelly....
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.52,0:31:07.87,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.63,0:31:11.32,中文,,0,0,0,,到我这儿来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.64,0:31:25.72,中文,,0,0,0,,到我这儿来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:40.62,0:31:43.11,中文,,0,0,0,,到我这儿来 凯莉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come to me, kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.29,0:31:55.81,中文,,0,0,0,,凯莉\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Kelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.50,0:32:00.53,中文,,0,0,0,,到我这儿来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Come to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.44,0:32:08.38,中文,,0,0,0,,看着我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.16,0:32:13.88,中文,,0,0,0,,尽情庆祝吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Rejoice.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.28,0:32:20.36,中文,,0,0,0,,尽情拥抱你光荣的命运\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Embrace your glorious fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.69,0:32:27.31,中文,,0,0,0,,嘿 魅力先生 记得要提醒我下次不要理你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey Mr. Charming, remind me to ignore you next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.31,0:32:30.80,中文,,0,0,0,,当然 下次会的 我们会用你的方式\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Sure, next time I will. We'll do it your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.80,0:32:33.84,中文,,0,0,0,,叫喊的 杀出一条血路\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}We'll shout, yell, shoot our way in.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.84,0:32:35.56,中文,,0,0,0,,我本来有个更好的机会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Yeah, well I had a better chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.07,0:32:37.40,中文,,0,0,0,,停下来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.99,0:32:41.31,中文,,0,0,0,,转过身来\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Turn around.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.19,0:32:56.43,中文,,0,0,0,,放松\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.19,0:32:58.57,中文,,0,0,0,,我会让你们走的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm letting you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.12,0:33:06.24,中文,,0,0,0,,我的老板已经误入歧途了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}My employer is... misguided.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.25,0:33:08.71,中文,,0,0,0,,那可不是一句 误入歧途 就能形容的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Misguided is not the bloody word I would use.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:08.71,0:33:10.10,中文,,0,0,0,,我不太认同他所做的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't agree with what he's doing,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.11,0:33:13.17,中文,,0,0,0,,我觉得我很难执行这种命令\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}so I can hardly carry out an order to kill the people
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.17,0:33:14.81,中文,,0,0,0,,去杀那些试图纠正的人\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}who are trying to make it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.72,0:33:18.56,中文,,0,0,0,,你的朋友们不会告发你吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Won't your friends here tell on you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.84,0:33:22.12,中文,,0,0,0,,他们忠诚于我\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Their loyalty is to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.36,0:33:24.36,中文,,0,0,0,,那你为什么不如加入我们\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Then why don't you all join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.36,0:33:26.54,中文,,0,0,0,,帮助我们做正确的事情\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Help us make this right.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.10,0:33:31.40,中文,,0,0,0,,去吧 趁你还有机会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go. While you have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.45,0:33:44.57,中文,,0,0,0,,快走\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.05,0:34:00.27,中文,,0,0,0,,戴安\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Diane?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.80,0:37:25.62,中文,,0,0,0,,现在能确定我们想法正确的唯一途径就是下到那儿去\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The only way to ensure we're right is go down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.93,0:37:40.15,中文,,0,0,0,,已经很晚了 我有点担心你\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's night. I was worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.02,0:37:45.25,中文,,0,0,0,,没事的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.97,0:37:55.80,中文,,0,0,0,,有没有想过我们是唯一幸运的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Guess we're not the only ones that struck out, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.80,0:37:58.24,中文,,0,0,0,,-没有找到你的妻子吗 -呃 你还在这儿啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- No luck with the wife, huh? - Oh, you're still here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.17,0:38:01.70,中文,,0,0,0,,准确地说是谁邀请你到这儿来的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who invited you here, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.44,0:38:06.68,中文,,0,0,0,,她在这里和我们一样\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}She's here just like the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.86,0:38:08.11,中文,,0,0,0,,谁让你负责的啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Who put you in charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.11,0:38:10.79,中文,,0,0,0,,疾控中心的主任\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}The director of the Centers for Disease control put me in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.80,0:38:12.53,中文,,0,0,0,,你知道什么啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.02,0:38:15.95,中文,,0,0,0,,我才不稀罕 如果你不欢迎我的话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I don't need this shit. If you don't want me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.96,0:38:18.25,中文,,0,0,0,,那绝对没有问题 我会走的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}That's absolutely no problem. I am gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.25,0:38:21.29,中文,,0,0,0,,嗨 嗨 嗨 这不是他的决定\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Hey, hey, hey. It's not his decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.29,0:38:24.62,中文,,0,0,0,,不要理他 他无权代表我们所有人说话\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Alright? Just ignore him. He doesn't speak for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.14,0:38:26.98,中文,,0,0,0,,外面太危险了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.72,0:38:29.94,中文,,0,0,0,,至少要等到天亮啊\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}At least just wait 'til morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.87,0:38:33.16,中文,,0,0,0,,我宁可去外面争取机会\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I would rather take my chances out there
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.16,0:38:35.72,中文,,0,0,0,,也不要和你们这些混蛋困在这里\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Than be stuck in here with you assholes!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.16,0:38:44.10,中文,,0,0,0,,这下好了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Great.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.10,0:38:47.13,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜 去外面争取机会应该是不错的选择\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You got a better idea out there, be my guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.58,0:38:51.82,中文,,0,0,0,,爸爸\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.24,0:38:58.21,中文,,0,0,0,,-嗨 儿子 -你找到妈妈了吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Hey, buddy. - Did you find mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.39,0:39:06.14,中文,,0,0,0,,古德温泽博士 我和诺亚正准备\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Dr. Goodweather, Nora and I were just about
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.14,0:39:08.87,中文,,0,0,0,,去我们发现的地方找一下  -稍等一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- to go over what we discovered... - Just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.96,0:39:32.08,中文,,0,0,0,,你们还没有找到她吗\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You... didn't find her?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.23,0:39:42.39,中文,,0,0,0,,没有 只是找到了她的手机\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}No. Look, I uh... I did find her phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.22,0:39:47.74,中文,,0,0,0,,我猜她是把手机丢了 那意味着什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I guess she lost it. What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.84,0:39:53.49,中文,,0,0,0,,扎克 我不能放弃\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}I'm not giving up, Zack.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.29,0:40:00.66,中文,,0,0,0,,或许这就是她为什么没有呼救了\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Maybe this is why she hasn't called.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.53,0:40:10.05,中文,,0,0,0,,-1230 -我知道\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- 1230. - I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.16,0:40:17.08,中文,,0,0,0,,这个是我们家在费城的地址\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It was the street address at our place in Philly
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.08,0:40:18.99,中文,,0,0,0,,那里我还在上医学院\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}when I was at medical school.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.29,0:40:23.22,中文,,0,0,0,,我们一起买东西的地方\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}First place we bought together.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.28,0:41:02.55,中文,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.67,0:41:05.00,中文,,0,0,0,,继续\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.60,0:41:12.02,中文,,0,0,0,,-继续  -快点\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Keep going! - Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.19,0:41:18.46,中文,,0,0,0,,-这就是你想要的 对吗  -妈妈 不会吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- It's what you wanted, right? - Mom, seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.44,0:41:21.65,中文,,0,0,0,,-在后院  -什么\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Back deck. - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.65,0:41:23.20,中文,,0,0,0,,去后院看一下\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Check the back deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.99,0:41:31.37,中文,,0,0,0,,惊喜吧\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}Surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.78,0:41:35.01,中文,,0,0,0,,-你喜欢它吗 -我喜欢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Do you like it? - I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.62,0:41:39.36,中文,,0,0,0,,-被我骗了吧  -是的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- I got you good, didn't I? - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.37,0:41:42.53,中文,,0,0,0,,-生日快乐 扎克  -谢谢\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}- Happy birthday, Z. - Thanks so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.53,0:41:45.91,中文,,0,0,0,,你是世上最好的妈妈了 我超喜欢蓝色\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}You're the best mom, ever! I love the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.99,0:41:48.34,中文,,0,0,0,,这正是我想要的\N{\3c&H000000&\fs25}It's exactly what I wanted...
